high_descs: Turn right and turn left to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the spoon to the left of the plate.
Turn around and walk to the counter with the microwave.
Place the spoon in front of the tomato on the left side of the counter.
Walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the spoon from the sink.
Walk back over to the counter with the microwave.
Put the spoon down on the counter to the left of the first spoon.
anns.task_desc: To move two spoons to the counter with the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the metal table spoon off of the counter.
Walk to the microwave that is behind you.
Put the spoon on the counter in front of the tomato in front of you.
Walk to the sink that is behind you.
Pick up the metal spoon out of the sink.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the microwave.
Put the metal spoon on the counter next to the other spoon.
anns.task_desc: Move two spoons to a counter.

high_descs: Take a step to the right and face the right end of the counter.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave stand.
Place the spoon on the left side of the microwave stand.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the spoon in the right side of the sink.
Turn around and step forward to face the microwave stand.
Place the spoon on the microwave stand with the other spoon.
anns.task_desc: To place two spoon on the microwave stand.
